      | This guidance is to help teachers and school leaders understand the
        digital approaches they can use to teach pupils remotely during the
        coronavirus outbreak.

    h3.govuk-heading-m What to consider

    p.govuk-body
      | To ensure you choose the best approach:

    ul.govuk-list.govuk-list--bullet
      li make sure the focus is on the teaching method and learning rather than technology
      li consider the skill level of the person using the approach
      li assess pupils’ education environments
      li consider the tools you already have
      li incorporate learning using physical copies of textbooks or booklets if pupils already have them

    p.govuk-body
      | Each school is different and the best approach for each will differ.

